high_descs: Walk over to the microwave on your right.
Take the sweet potato out of the microwave then close the door.
Turn left and walk towards the door, then turn left and walk up to the fridge.
Put the sweet potato in the fridge for a couple seconds and let it get cold, then take it out of the fridge.
Turn left and walk towards the counter, then hang a left and walk up to the white table against the wall.
Put the cold sweet potato on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold sweet potato on a white table.

high_descs: move forwards to the microwave ahead on the right
grab the potato out of the microwave
turn left and walk over to the fridge on the left side of the room at the end of the room
place the potato inside of the fridge there, let it cool, then take it back out
turn around and walk over to the center of the white long table against the wall at the end of the room
place the potato down on the table there in between the salt shakers
anns.task_desc: place a cooled potato down on top of the table

high_descs: Turn right to face the sink, then face the microwave on the left.
Open the microwave and take out the potato. Shut the door.
Carry the potato and turn to the left. Then turn left to find the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the potato inside. Shut the door, then open it. Take out the potato and shut the door.
Carry the potato and turn to the left and then left again to face the white table.
Place the potato on the white table, close to the front.
anns.task_desc: Chill a potato and place on the table.
